==前奏==
=== 親歐盟示威與亞努科維奇政府下台 ===
{{main|烏克蘭親歐盟示威運動}}
2013年11月21日，乌克兰政府决定，暂停有关与欧盟签署联系国协定的准备工作，同时表示将加强与俄罗斯等其他[[独联体|独联体]]国家的经贸关系。乌克兰社会和政治危机自此爆发，觸發[[烏克蘭親歐盟示威運動|烏克蘭親歐盟示威運動]]。
<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2013-11/22/c_125743099.htm|title=欧盟对乌克兰暂停签署联系国协定表示失望-新华网|publisher=News.xinhuanet.com|date=|accessdate=2015-12-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105131415/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2013-11/22/c_125743099.htm|archivedate=2015-11-05}}</ref>至2014年2月22日，烏克蘭國會解除[[亞努科維奇|亞努科維奇]]的總統職權使其下台，佔領獨立廣場的示威者衝進政府大樓並控制基輔。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-02-22 |title=Ukraine Protestors Seize Kiev As President Flees |url=http://world.time.com/2014/02/22/ukraines-president-flees-protestors-capture-kiev/ |deadurl=no |newspaper=時代雜誌 |location=USA |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221013831/http://world.time.com/2014/02/22/ukraines-president-flees-protestors-capture-kiev/ |archivedate=2015-02-21 |access-date=2015-02-23 }}</ref>不過當時亞努科維奇稱這是一場政變，俄羅斯亦質疑此事的合法性，認為是武力政變，拒絕承認反對派國會議長[[亞歷山大·圖奇諾夫|亞歷山大·圖奇諾夫]]領導的烏克蘭臨時政府<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2015-02-25 |title=Russia refuses to recognise Ukraine government |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-02-25/russia-refuses-to-recognise-ukraine-government/5284182 |deadurl=no |newspaper=澳大利亚广播公司 |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150303121536/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-02-25/russia-refuses-to-recognise-ukraine-government/5284182 |archivedate=2015-03-03 |access-date=2015-02-23 }}</ref>；但[[歐盟|歐盟]]、[[美國|美國]]及[[聯合國|聯合國]]都予以承認<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2015-02-24 |title=US, EU, UN recognize Ukraine’s new government |url=http://tass.ru/en/world/720696 |deadurl=no |newspaper=俄通社 |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150223135426/http://tass.ru/en/world/720696 |archivedate=2015-02-23 |access-date=2015-02-23 }}</ref>。之后亚努科维奇被迫逃亡俄罗斯，图奇诺夫成为乌克兰代理总统。

=== 克里米亞公投獨立 ===
{{main|2014年克里米亞歸屬公投}}
2月22－23日，俄罗斯总统普京通宵召开国安会议，商讨解救被废黜的亚努科维奇。会议结束时普京说：“我们一定要开始设法让克里米亚回归俄罗斯。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/video/news/video-1165795/Vladimir-Putin-admits-plot-Russia-annex-Crimea.html |title=Vladimir Putin admits plot Russia annex Crimea |access-date=2022-05-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>在俄罗斯方面制作的[[宣传|宣传]]影片《[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t42-71RpRgI 克里米亞回家之路] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t42-71RpRgI |date=20201124155739 }}》中有詳細說明</ref>。自2月26日起，俄羅斯駐軍联合克里米亞親俄議員開始逐步控制克里米亞半島。2月27日，广泛被认为是俄罗斯特种部队的无徽章军人占领了克里米亚最高议会以及辛菲罗波尔的市政大厅。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/28/world/europe/crimea-ukraine.html?_r=0|title=Gunmen Seize Government Buildings in Crimea|author=Andrew Higgins|author2=Steven Erlanger|work=The New York Times|date=27 February 2014|accessdate=25 February 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217060240/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/28/world/europe/crimea-ukraine.html?_r=0|archive-date=2014-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://estonianworld.com/security/lessons-identified-crimea-estonias-national-defence-model-meet-needs/|agency=Estonian World|title=Lessons identified in Crimea – does Estonia's national defence model meet our needs?|date=5 May 2014|accessdate=12 June 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702061418/http://estonianworld.com/security/lessons-identified-crimea-estonias-national-defence-model-meet-needs/|archive-date=2015-07-02|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在军人占领的时候，召开了一次紧急议会<ref name=interfax27feb>http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/193292.html {{Wayback|url=http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/193292.html |date=20150626153118 }} Number of Crimean deputies present at referendum resolution vote unclear]. [[Interfax-Ukraine|Interfax-Ukraine]], 27 February 2014.</ref><ref name=reuters13mar>[http://in.reuters.com/article/2014/03/13/ukraine-crisis-russia-aksyonov-idINL6N0M93AH20140313 RPT-INSIGHT: How the separatists delivered Crimea to Moscow] {{Wayback|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/2014/03/13/ukraine-crisis-russia-aksyonov-idINL6N0M93AH20140313 |date=20150626101233 }}. [[Reuters|Reuters]], 13 March 2014.</ref>，决定结束现有克里米亚政府统治，选[[謝爾蓋·阿克肖諾夫|謝爾蓋·阿克肖諾夫]]作为新任[[克里米亞部長會議主席|克里米亞部長會議主席]]（政府总理）<ref name="The Christian Science Monitor">[http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Europe/2014/0227/Crimea-sets-date-for-autonomy-vote-amid-gunmen-anti-Kiev-protests-video Crimea sets date for autonomy vote amid gunmen, anti-Kiev protests] {{Wayback|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Europe/2014/0227/Crimea-sets-date-for-autonomy-vote-amid-gunmen-anti-Kiev-protests-video |date=20150702122904 }}, (27 February 2014).</ref> 。阿克肖諾夫属于「俄罗斯统一党」，在上一次选举只得了4%的选票。随后，克里米亞議會亦宣布在克里米亞舉行[[2014年克里米亞歸屬公投|全民公投]]。全民公投於3月16日舉行，當地居民以俄羅斯族為多數，亦有部分克里米亞韃靼人抵制公投<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-03-17 |title=Crimean Tatars Appear to Boycott Voting |url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702304747404579443341954329348 |deadurl=no |newspaper=華爾街日報 |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150223134935/http://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702304747404579443341954329348 |archivedate=2015-02-23 |access-date=2015-02-23 }}</ref>。最後克里米亚政府宣称97%的贊成票支持克里米亞獨立。公投前夕，聯合國安理會表決一項聲明公投無效且不影響克里米亞地位，維護烏克蘭主權、獨立、統一及領土完整的無約束力決議，其中俄羅斯運用了她的否決權令決議未獲通過<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.un.org/zh/documents/view_doc.asp?symbol=S%2F2014%2F189 |title=決議草案文件 |access-date=2020-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140507090226/http://www.un.org/zh/documents/view_doc.asp?symbol=S%2F2014%2F189 |archive-date=2014-05-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.un.org/zh/documents/view_doc.asp?symbol=S%2FPV.7138 |title=會議記錄 |access-date=2020-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140507093429/http://www.un.org/zh/documents/view_doc.asp?symbol=S%2FPV.7138 |archive-date=2014-05-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。公投結果公布後歐盟、美國等國家譴責俄羅斯，烏克蘭及美國等國家均不承認此次公投，但克里米亞於3月17日即宣布獨立並要求加入俄羅斯聯邦，於3月18日簽署加入聯邦的條約，並於3月21日在普京簽署法案下正式生效。3月27日，聯合國大會則以100票贊成，11票反对，58票棄權通過了一項「支持烏克蘭領土完整，克里米亞公投無效」的無約束力議案。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.un.org/en/story/2014/03/464812-backing-ukraines-territorial-integrity-un-assembly-declares-crimea-referendum |title=Backing Ukraine's territorial integrity, UN Assembly declares Crimea referendum invalid |access-date=2014-03-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-03-27 |title=聯合國大會決議 不接受克里米亞公投 |url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140328000018-260408 |deadurl=no |newspaper=中國時報 |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150223134356/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140328000018-260408 |archivedate=2015-02-23 |access-date=2015-02-23 }}</ref>
 
克里米亞入俄後，愈來愈多居於當地的烏克蘭人離開並轉往烏克蘭其他區域<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-03-20 |title=Over 1,200 people leave Crimea for Ukraine |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/over-1200-people-leave-crimea-for-ukraine-340162.html |deadurl=no |newspaper=基輔報 |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225133056/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/over-1200-people-leave-crimea-for-ukraine-340162.html |archivedate=2015-02-25 |access-date=2015-02-25 }}</ref>。[[联合国难民事务高级专员办事处|联合国难民事务高级专员办事处]]於5月20日表示已統計到10000人進行遷移，並急需社區服務及住所，這些遷移的居民主要都是克里米亞韃靼人，他們離開的原因主要都是感到不安全及怕會受逼害<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.unhcr.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/search?page=search&docid=537b31b49&query=crimea |title=UNHCR says internal displacement rising in Ukraine |access-date=2015-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225132813/http://www.unhcr.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/search?page=search&docid=537b31b49&query=crimea |archive-date=2015-02-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==冲突时间表==
=== 東烏克蘭親俄示威及公投獨立 ===
{{main|新俄羅斯}} 

[[File:2014-05-11._Референдум_в_Донецке_017.jpg|thumb]]
東烏克蘭各地在克里米亞公投後亦爆發親俄示威，他們亦要求在東烏克蘭舉行像克里米亞一樣的公投，加入俄羅斯聯邦。示威者屢次與警察發生衝突，更於4月初攻佔了[[頓涅茨克|頓涅茨克]]的政府行政大樓及[[盧甘斯克|盧甘斯克]]的安全部門大樓，並宣布建立「[[頓涅茨克人民共和國|頓涅茨克人民共和國]]」及「[[盧甘斯克人民共和國|盧甘斯克人民共和國]]」，並決定在5月11日舉行公投決定是否獨立。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-04-07 |title=Ukraine crisis escalates as pro-Russia activists declare independence in Donetsk |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/apr/07/ukraine-crisis-pro-russia-activists-declare-independence-donetsk |deadurl=no |newspaper=The Guardian |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408063607/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/apr/07/ukraine-crisis-pro-russia-activists-declare-independence-donetsk |archivedate=2014-04-08 |accessdate=2015-02-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-04-06 |title=烏克蘭東部城市爆發親俄示威|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/04/140406_ukraine_protest |deadurl= |newspaper=BBC中文網 |location= |archiveurl= |archivedate= |accessdate=2015-02-25}}</ref>頓涅茨克州南部城市馬里烏波爾更在4月17日爆發親俄武裝份子與烏克蘭軍隊的衝突，烏克蘭內政部長阿瓦科夫聲稱有親武武裝分子襲擊當地國民衞隊基地，烏軍作出反擊擊斃三名武裝分子。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-04-17 |title=烏克蘭危機：東部軍事基地衝突三人死亡|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/04/140417_ukraine_clash |deadurl= |newspaper=BBC中文網 |location= |archiveurl= |archivedate= |accessdate=2015-02-25 }}</ref>接著東烏克蘭各地亦繼續有親俄份子佔領政府大樓的事件。親俄武裝份子亦控制了[[斯拉維揚斯克_(烏克蘭)|斯拉維揚斯克]]，烏克蘭政府宣稱要是進行反恐行動，自4月起派軍試圖重奪而與武裝份子發生多次激烈戰鬥。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-04-15 |script-title=en:Ukraine as it happened: Kyiv starts “anti-terror” operation retaking Kramatorsk airfield |url=http://www.euronews.com/2014/04/15/live-ukraine-germany-urges-russia-to-distance-itself-unlawful-protesters-in-/ |deadurl=no |newspaper=euronews.com |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225143900/http://www.euronews.com/2014/04/15/live-ukraine-germany-urges-russia-to-distance-itself-unlawful-protesters-in-/ |archivedate=2015-02-25 |accessdate=2015-02-25 }}</ref>

東烏克蘭武裝份子於5月11日如期舉行他們控制下的獨立公投，烏克蘭國民衞隊為了阻止公投，在公投當日試圖控制[[紅軍城_(烏克蘭)|紅軍城]]市政厅，遂與建築外群眾發生衝突，國民衞隊在衝突中更向群眾開火，至少造成一死兩傷，但公投還是繼續下去<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-05-11 |title=Ukraine Guardsmen Opened Fire Amid Referendum Vote, Rebels Say |url=http://time.com/95478/ukraine-violence-referendum/ |deadurl=no |newspaper=時代雜誌 |location=USA |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130055109/http://time.com/95478/ukraine-violence-referendum/ |archivedate=2015-01-30 |access-date=2015-02-26 }}</ref>。親俄部隊隨後宣布公投結果，稱於頓涅茨克州有89%的人支持獨立；盧甘斯克更有96%，親俄份子遂宣布兩州正式獨立並申請加入俄羅斯聯邦。然而烏克蘭一直不承認這場公投，圖奇洛夫稱這場公投非法，乃是掩蓋謀殺、綁架、暴力和各種嚴罪行的宣傳；烏克蘭國家安全委員會主席{{link-uk|安德里·帕魯比|Парубій_Андрій_Володимирович}}更稱這場公投是普京的宣傳鬧劇，如同[[希特勒|希特勒]]於[[德奧合併|奧地利所作的公投]]；歐盟及美國亦指這場公投並不合法，拒絕承認。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-05-12 |title='Referendums' in eastern Ukraine have no legal consequences - Turchynov |url=http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/204345.html |deadurl=no |newspaper=The Guardian |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402144734/http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/204345.html |archivedate=2015-04-02 |access-date=2015-03-02 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-05-12 |title=Ukraine: pro-Russia separatists set for victory in eastern region referendum |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/may/11/eastern-ukraine-referendum-donetsk-luhansk |deadurl=no |newspaper=The Guardian |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328215000/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/may/11/eastern-ukraine-referendum-donetsk-luhansk |archivedate=2015-03-28 |access-date=2015-02-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Denyer |first1=Simon |last2=Nemstova |date=2014-05-11 |title=Eastern Ukrainians vote for self-rule in referendum opposed by West |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/ukraines-rebels-say-they-are-seeking-a-mandate-not-independence-in-referendum/2014/05/11/ac02688a-d8dc-11e3-aae8-c2d44bd79778_story.html |deadurl=no |newspaper=華盛頓郵報 |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215124248/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/ukraines-rebels-say-they-are-seeking-a-mandate-not-independence-in-referendum/2014/05/11/ac02688a-d8dc-11e3-aae8-c2d44bd79778_story.html |archivedate=2015-02-15 |access-date=2015-02-26 }}</ref>俄羅斯總統府則發表聲明對兩州人民在公投中表達的意願表示尊重，期望基輔與兩州代表們以和平原則溝通並執行公投結果，停止暴力。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-05-11 |title=Referendum results in Donetsk and Lugansk Regions show landslide support for self-rule |url=http://rt.com/news/158276-referendum-results-east-ukraine/ |deadurl=no |newspaper=[[RT電視台|RT電視台]] |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217080358/http://rt.com/news/158276-referendum-results-east-ukraine/ |archivedate=2015-02-17 |access-date=2015-02-26 }}</ref>俄羅斯總理[[德米特里·阿纳托利耶维奇·梅德韦杰夫|梅德韋傑夫]]則表示俄國並無義務拒絕插手當地事務，不願保証會確保烏克蘭領土完整。不過，俄羅斯並沒有正面承認兩州獨立，亦沒有正面回應其入俄申請。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-05-21 |title=Medvedev Says Russia Has No Obligation to Stay Out of East Ukraine |url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/medvedev-says-russia-has-no-obligation-to-stay-out-of-east-ukraine/500564.html |deadurl=no |newspaper=莫斯科時報 |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226132657/http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/medvedev-says-russia-has-no-obligation-to-stay-out-of-east-ukraine/500564.html |archivedate=2015-02-26 |access-date=2015-02-26 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-05-21 |title=Russia declines to recognize separatist victories |url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/news/world/2014/05/12/russia-stops-short-recognizing-east-ukraine-independence-votes/Rudvxf5ebHm6mKg9UCKlcK/story.html |deadurl=no |newspaper=[[波士頓環球報|波士頓環球報]] |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226131907/http://www.bostonglobe.com/news/world/2014/05/12/russia-stops-short-recognizing-east-ukraine-independence-votes/Rudvxf5ebHm6mKg9UCKlcK/story.html |archivedate=2015-02-26 |access-date=2015-02-26 }}</ref>

