協議生效前數小時馬里烏波爾等地據報仍然有衝突，烏克蘭戰機仍在轟炸武裝份子陣地<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2015-09-05 |title=烏克蘭交戰雙方達成初步停火協議 |trans-title= |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/09/140905_russia_ukraine_talk |newspaper=BBC中文網 |location= |access-date=2015-03-03 }}</ref>。而在生效翌日，雖然俄烏總統都報稱停火已大致執行，但作為衝突熱點的馬里烏波爾及頓涅茨克機場仍然發生衝突，馬里烏波爾據報發生炮擊，當時由政府控制的頓涅茨克機場附近亦有炮擊和槍擊<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-09-07 |title=Ukraine crisis: Shelling near Mariupol threatens truce |trans-title= |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-29097836 |language= |newspaper=BBC |location= |access-date=2015-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217085716/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-29097836 |archive-date=2015-02-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-09-07 |title=Artillery attack challenges ceasefire in east Ukraine |trans-title= |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/09/06/us-ukraine-crisis-idUSKBN0GZ18D20140906 |language=en |newspaper=路透社 |location= |access-date=2015-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150531090403/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/09/06/us-ukraine-crisis-idUSKBN0GZ18D20140906 |archive-date=2015-05-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>9月13日上午，烏克蘭軍方宣布他們擊退了武裝份子對頓涅茨克機場的一次攻擊，而當地每天亦不斷傳出炮火聲。頓涅茨克武裝份子領袖指責烏克蘭多次違反停火協議，烏軍則指控武裝份子多次主動攻擊烏軍據點<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-09-17 |title=Ukraine rebels say ceasefire has broken down |trans-title= |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/ukraine/11102111/Ukraine-rebels-say-ceasefire-has-broken-down.html |language= |newspaper=The Telegraph |location= |access-date=2015-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402121749/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/ukraine/11102111/Ukraine-rebels-say-ceasefire-has-broken-down.html |archive-date=2015-04-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[日丹尼夫卡|日丹尼夫卡]]等地駐守的烏軍據報亦遭武裝分子攻擊，爆發激烈衝突<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-09-16 |title=“快速三叉戟-2014”多国军演在乌克兰举行 |trans-title= |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2014/09-16/6593568.shtml |language= |newspaper=中國新聞網 |location= |access-date=2016-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305082313/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2014/09-16/6593568.shtml |archive-date=2016-03-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，哥羅夫卡、傑巴利采韋、基洛夫斯克、多庫恰耶夫等多處地方傳出烏政府軍砲擊事件。雙方不斷的軍事衝突令明斯克協議中的停火條款面臨挑戰。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2015-09-14 |title=Despite Cease-Fire, Fighting Escalates in Eastern Ukraine City |trans-title= |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/09/15/world/europe/deadly-fighting-in-donetsk-ukraine.html |newspaper=紐約時報 |location= |access-date=2015-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414024604/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/09/15/world/europe/deadly-fighting-in-donetsk-ukraine.html |archive-date=2015-04-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.eastday.com/eastday/13news/auto/news/world/u7ai2539026_K4.html |title=乌克兰停火协议面临挑战 乌俄相互指责升级 |access-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025075256/http://news.eastday.com/eastday/13news/auto/news/world/u7ai2539026_K4.html |archive-date=2014-10-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[歐洲安全與合作組織|歐洲安全與合作組織]]、俄、烏政府及武裝份子代表遂於9月20日加簽和平備忘錄，訂明雙方須撤走各自的「外國僱庸軍」，設立寛30公里的非軍事區，重型武器自前線後撤15公里的條款。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-09-20 |title=乌克兰政府与亲俄武装明斯克和谈达协议 |trans-title= |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2014/09/140920_ukraine_rebels_minsk_talks |language= |newspaper=BBC |location= |access-date=2015-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140928193745/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2014/09/140920_ukraine_rebels_minsk_talks |archive-date=2014-09-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
 
繼8月22日的第一批人道主義車輛進入烏克蘭後，9月13日俄羅斯再次在沒得烏克蘭政府准許，亦沒有紅十字會委員會人員陪同下派遣第二批人道主義物資的卡車越過俄烏邊境，並得親俄武裝份子護送。俄羅斯宣稱這些車輛對烏克蘭東部民眾發放運送一批共2000噸人道主義援助物資，包括食品、藥品、醫療設備等，<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-09-12 |title=Москва и Московская область отправили гуманитарную помощь на восток Украины |trans-title= |url=http://www.interfax.ru/world/390821 |language= |newspaper=INTERFAX |location= |access-date=2015-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214015433/http://www.interfax.ru/world/390821 |archive-date=2015-02-14 |dead-url=no }}據此俄方報導提及，280輛卡車運載包括400噸穀物、100噸糖、62.4噸嬰兒食品、54噸醫療設備和藥品、12000個睡袋，以及69套不同的發電機</ref>但烏克蘭政府一直為防俄軍乘機入侵而一直拒絕車輛進入，及後對於俄方車輛再次擅自穿越邊界表示抗議，堅持人道物資該交給紅十字會接收運輸及派發，並指物資清單中有部分物品不能視為人道物資；美國表示俄羅斯人道主義援助違反國際法，人道主義車輛必須烏克蘭政府許可同意下能進境。不過俄羅斯一直否認車隊是乘機入侵，反而顧慮到烏東人道主義危機日益惡化，在烏克蘭一直阻止下才不等烏方許可而下令車隊前進。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-11-01 |title=烏克蘭指責人道主義車隊進入東部 |trans-title= |url=http://world.people.com.cn/n/2014/1101/c157278-25951110.html |language= |newspaper=人民網 |location= |access-date=2015-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214011430/http://world.people.com.cn/n/2014/1101/c157278-25951110.html |archive-date=2015-02-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>而及後俄羅斯仍然多次派出車輛宣稱運載人道物資到烏克蘭，至2015年1月8日已輸送了11批。<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2015-01-08 |title=俄罗斯向乌克兰提供第11批人道主义援助物资 |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-01/08/c_1113930552.htm |language= |newspaper=新華網 |location= |access-date=2015-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214210646/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-01/08/c_1113930552.htm |archive-date=2015-02-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
 
