== 人道關注 ==
{{Main article|烏克蘭頓巴斯戰爭與人道主義危機|頓巴斯種族滅絕指控}}
[[聯合國|聯合國]]觀察到隸屬於[[頓涅茨克人民共和國|頓涅茨克人民共和國]]和[[盧甘斯克人民共和國|盧甘斯克人民共和國]]的（武裝）支持者控制的領土上的[[人權|人權]]狀況出現“令人震驚的惡化”。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Ukraine crisis: UN sounds alarm on human rights in east|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-27438422|newspaper=BBC News|date=2014-05-16|accessdate=2022-03-06|language=en-GB|archive-date=2014-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140516231435/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-27438422|dead-url=no}}</ref> 聯合國報告記載許多主要由頓涅茨克人民共和國軍隊實施的有針對性的殺戮、酷刑和綁架案件。<ref name="un">{{Cite book|url=http://www.ohchr.org/Documents/Countries/UA/HRMMUReport15May2014.pdf|title=Report on the human rights situation in Ukraine|date=15 May 2014|publisher=Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights|access-date=2022-03-06|archive-date=2014-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517153207/http://www.ohchr.org/Documents/Countries/UA/HRMMUReport15May2014.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 聯合國還報告了對記者和國際觀察員的威脅、襲擊和綁架，以及對烏克蘭統一支持者的毆打和襲擊。<ref name="un2">{{Cite book|url=http://www.ohchr.org/Documents/Countries/UA/HRMMUReport15May2014.pdf|title=Report on the human rights situation in Ukraine|date=15 May 2014|publisher=Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights|access-date=2022-03-06|archive-date=2014-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517153207/http://www.ohchr.org/Documents/Countries/UA/HRMMUReport15May2014.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 俄羅斯政府及其支持者批評了這些報導，並說它們是“出於政治動機”。<ref name="un3">{{Cite book|url=http://www.ohchr.org/Documents/Countries/UA/HRMMUReport15May2014.pdf|title=Report on the human rights situation in Ukraine|date=15 May 2014|publisher=Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights|access-date=2022-03-06|archive-date=2014-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517153207/http://www.ohchr.org/Documents/Countries/UA/HRMMUReport15May2014.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[人權觀察|人權觀察]]的一份報告稱，“烏克蘭東部的反基輔部隊正在綁架、攻擊和騷擾他們懷疑支持烏克蘭政府或認為不受歡迎的人…反基輔叛亂分子正在使用毆打和綁架來傳遞這樣的信息：任何不支持他們的人最好閉嘴或離開”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ukraine: Anti-Kiev Forces Running Amok|url=https://www.hrw.org/news/2014/05/23/ukraine-anti-kiev-forces-running-amok|access-date=2022-03-06|date=2014-05-23|work=Human Rights Watch|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220221180655/https://www.hrw.org/news/2014/05/23/ukraine-anti-kiev-forces-running-amok|dead-url=no}}</ref> 烏克蘭方面，例如[[奧列格·利亞什科|奧列格·利亞什科]]（Oleh Lyashko）所統帥的民兵和艾達爾（Aidar）[[烏克蘭地方防衛作戰營|地方防衛作戰營]]也多次毆打、綁架和可能處決當地居民。<ref name="#1">{{Cite news|date=10 September 2014|title=Ukrainian Nationalist Volunteers Committing 'ISIS-Style' War Crimes|work=[[Newsweek|Newsweek]]|url=http://www.newsweek.com/evidence-war-crimes-committed-ukrainian-nationalist-volunteers-grows-269604|accessdate=2022-03-06|archive-date=2022-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220223200722/https://www.newsweek.com/evidence-war-crimes-committed-ukrainian-nationalist-volunteers-grows-269604|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AMsdsd">{{Cite press release|title=Impunity reigns for abductions and ill-treatment by pro-Kyiv vigilantes in eastern Ukraine|date=6 August 2014|publisher=Amnesty International|url=http://www.amnestyusa.org/news/news-item/impunity-reigns-for-abductions-and-ill-treatment-by-pro-kyiv-vigilantes-in-eastern-ukraine|access-date=9 August 2014|archive-date=2014-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810071542/http://www.amnestyusa.org/news/news-item/impunity-reigns-for-abductions-and-ill-treatment-by-pro-kyiv-vigilantes-in-eastern-ukraine|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]指出，親基輔的志願戰鬥群體經常阻止[[人道援助|人道主義援助]]進入烏克蘭東部。<ref name="#1"/>8月，親俄叛亂分子指揮官[[伊戈爾·斯特列爾科夫|伊戈爾·斯特列爾科夫]]的高級顧問伊戈爾·德魯茲說：“在緊急狀態下，我們曾多次開槍處決以防止混亂。因此，我們的部隊、那些從[[斯洛文尼亞|斯洛文尼亞]]撤出的人，紀律嚴明”。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Ukraine crisis: Rebel adviser 'admits executions'|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-28619599|newspaper=BBC News|date=2014-08-02|accessdate=2022-03-06|language=en-GB|archive-date=2022-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220115023328/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-28619599|dead-url=no}}</ref> 伊戈爾·斯特列爾科夫到2015年底，在頓涅茨克人民共和國和盧甘斯克人民共和國合併的領土內有79個地方關押了被綁架的平民和戰俘。<ref>{{Cite web|title=На неконтролируемой Украиной территории Донбасса есть 79 неофициальных мест незаконного содержания людей|url=http://interfax.com.ua/news/general/307388.html|access-date=29 November 2015|publisher=Interfax Ukraine|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208111736/http://interfax.com.ua/news/general/307388.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處|聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處]] (OHCHR) 於 2014 年 7 月 28 日發布的一份報告稱，根據“保守估計”，自4月中旬以來，至少有1129名平民在戰鬥中喪生，至少3442人受傷。<ref name="IFadaf">{{Cite news|date=28 July 2014|title=1,129 civilians killed, 3,442 injured in Ukraine during anti-terrorist operation – UN report|work=Interfax-Ukraine News Agency|url=http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/215684.html|access-date=28 July 2014|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111145713/https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/215684.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="OHCHRrep">{{Cite press release|title=Intense fighting in eastern Ukraine 'extremely alarming', says Pillay, as UN releases new report|date=28 July 2014|publisher=Office of the High Commissioner for Human Rights|url=http://www.ohchr.org/EN/NewsEvents/Pages/Media.aspx?IsMediaPage=true&LangID=E|access-date=28 July 2014|archive-date=2022-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220218153024/https://www.ohchr.org/EN/NewsEvents/Pages/Media.aspx?IsMediaPage=true&LangID=E|dead-url=no}}</ref> 報告顯示，頓涅茨克州和盧甘斯克州的財產和基礎設施損失至少達 7.5 億美元。<ref name="OHCHRrep2">{{Cite press release|title=Intense fighting in eastern Ukraine 'extremely alarming', says Pillay, as UN releases new report|date=28 July 2014|publisher=Office of the High Commissioner for Human Rights|url=http://www.ohchr.org/EN/NewsEvents/Pages/Media.aspx?IsMediaPage=true&LangID=E|access-date=28 July 2014|archive-date=2022-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220218153024/https://www.ohchr.org/EN/NewsEvents/Pages/Media.aspx?IsMediaPage=true&LangID=E|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[人權觀察|人權觀察]]表示，烏克蘭政府軍、親烏克蘭政府準軍事組織和分離主義群體在襲擊平民區時使用了[[BM-21火箭炮|BM-21火箭炮]]，稱“在人口稠密地區不分青紅皂白地使用火箭彈違反了國際人道主義法或戰爭法，並可能構成戰爭罪”。<ref>{{Cite press release|title=Ukraine: Unguided Rockets Killing Civilians|date=24 July 2014|publisher=Human Rights Watch|url=https://www.hrw.org/news/2014/07/24/ukraine-unguided-rockets-killing-civilians|access-date=27 July 2014|archive-date=2014-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724231853/http://www.hrw.org/news/2014/07/24/ukraine-unguided-rockets-killing-civilians|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>"[https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/checkpoint/wp/2014/07/25/human-rights-watch-ukrainian-forces-are-rocketing-civilians/ Human Rights Watch: Ukrainian forces are rocketing civilians] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/checkpoint/wp/2014/07/25/human-rights-watch-ukrainian-forces-are-rocketing-civilians/ |date=20171020060301 }}". ''[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]''. 25 July 2014.</ref> 《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》報導說，平民的高死亡率“使烏克蘭東部的民眾對烏克蘭的親西方政府充滿怨恨”，這種情緒有助於“刺激招募”叛亂分子。<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Tavernise|first1=Sabrina|last2=Sneider|first2=Noah|date=28 July 2014|title=Enmity and Civilian Toll Rise in Ukraine While Attention Is Diverted|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/07/29/world/europe/civilian-death-toll-rise-in-ukraine.html|access-date=29 July 2014|archive-date=2021-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210917035416/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/07/29/world/europe/civilian-death-toll-rise-in-ukraine.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 到2015年1月上旬，儘管2014年9月上旬簽署了明斯克協議，但戰爭造成的死亡人數已上升至4707人。<ref name="UN14JAN">{{Cite press release|title=UN strongly deplores civilian deaths as Ukraine fighting continues|date=14 January 2015|publisher=United Nations News Centre|url=https://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=49794|access-date=15 January 2015|archive-date=2017-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171022142711/https://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=49794|dead-url=no}}</ref>

由於衝突，“接觸線”兩側的頓巴斯地區大片地區已被[[地雷|地雷]]和其他戰爭遺留爆炸物（ERW）污染。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ukraine's desperate attempt to defuse landmines – as more are planted|url=http://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2016/apr/04/ukraine-attempt-defuse-landmines-as-more-are-planted|access-date=2022-02-02|date=2016-04-04|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220219094703/https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2016/apr/04/ukraine-attempt-defuse-landmines-as-more-are-planted|dead-url=no}}</ref> 據駐烏克蘭的聯合國人道主義協調員稱，2020年，烏克蘭是世界上受地雷影響最嚴重的國家之一，自2014年衝突開始以來，已有近 1,200 起因地雷/戰爭遺留爆炸物造成的傷亡事件。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Landmines Still Pose a Threat to Two Million Ukrainians|url=https://ukraine.un.org/en/123917-landmines-still-pose-threat-two-million-ukrainians|access-date=2 February 2022|date=5 April 2021|website=United Nations Ukraine|archive-date=2022-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220224135714/https://ukraine.un.org/en/123917-landmines-still-pose-threat-two-million-ukrainians|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[聯合國兒童基金會|聯合國兒童基金會]]於 2019年12月發布的一份報告稱，有172名兒童因地雷和其他爆炸物受傷或死亡，超過750所教育設施遭到破壞或摧毀，430,000名兒童生活在與戰爭有關的心理創傷中。<ref>{{Cite web|title=430,000 children continue to bear the brunt of eastern Ukraine conflict|url=https://www.unicef.org/press-releases/430000-children-continue-bear-brunt-eastern-ukraine-conflict|access-date=2022-02-02|website=www.unicef.org|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220224152532/https://www.unicef.org/press-releases/430000-children-continue-bear-brunt-eastern-ukraine-conflict|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Children endure deadly legacy of landmines in eastern Ukraine|url=https://www.unicef.org/ukraine/en/stories/children-endure-deadly-legacy-landmines-eastern-ukraine|access-date=2022-02-02|website=www.unicef.org|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220203060201/https://www.unicef.org/ukraine/en/stories/children-endure-deadly-legacy-landmines-eastern-ukraine|dead-url=no}}</ref>

雖然俄方一直宣稱烏克蘭在這次衝突中有系統地消滅頓巴斯（親俄）人民，但[[歐洲安全與合作組織|歐洲安全與合作組織]]（OSCE）負責2014年起監測烏克蘭衝突的部門表示並沒有發現任何支持俄羅斯的「系統性滅絕」說法的證據。<ref>{{cite|url=https://www.dw.com/en/fact-check-russia-falsely-blames-ukraine-for-starting-war/a-60999948|title=Fact check: Russia falsely blames Ukraine for starting war|work=[[德國之聲|德國之聲]]|date=2022-03-03|accessdate=2022-03-30|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite|url=https://www.osce.org/special-monitoring-mission-to-ukraine|title=OSCE Special Monitoring Mission to Ukraine|work=[[歐洲安全與合作組織|歐洲安全與合作組織]]|accessdate=2022-03-30|language=en}}</ref>

